《'''父辈的土地'''》（{{lang-cy|Hen Wlad fy Nhadau}}）是[[威尔士|威尔士]]的传统[[国歌|国歌]]，作曲者[[埃文·詹姆斯|埃文·詹姆斯]]，作词者[[詹姆斯·詹姆斯|詹姆斯·詹姆斯]]。<ref name="Anthem genedlaethol">{{cite web |url=http://www.wales.com/en/content/cms/English/About_Wales/Music/WelshNationalAnthem/WelshNationalAnthem.aspx |title=Welsh National Anthem |publisher=Welsh Government |year=2014 |accessdate=24 May 2014 |work=wales.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423233819/http://www.wales.com/en/content/cms/English/About_Wales/Music/WelshNationalAnthem/WelshNationalAnthem.aspx |archivedate=2014年4月23日 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/music/sites/anthem/ |title=BBC Wales - Music - National Anthem |accessdate=2014-08-23 |archive-date=2014-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140802184602/http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/music/sites/anthem/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

